{"tid":2417363,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇人講我講］鮮浪潮15周年節目巡禮 Week 4","createTime":"2021-02-21T22:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T23:52:26.000Z","uid":376697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"11745908b946d597b9d5af81a678df4fc2cdb3e6","tid":2417363,"uid":376697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T22:46:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">FB post link:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116437285041244/posts/4064716206879979/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116437285041244%2Fposts%2F4064716206879979%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c07974ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116437285041244/posts/4064716206879979/?d=n</a></span><br />\n【鮮浪潮線上放映 #2月Week4片單】<br />\n「鮮浪潮15週年節目巡禮①︰歷屆優秀作品線上放映馬拉松」將於2至5月期間舉行，由2月1日開始，逢星期一、三、五於晚上8時播放精選短片，9時半映後談。<br />\n<br />\n#2月22日 #邊緣小人物<br />\n《他們的海》黃瑋納<br />\n《赤手》嚴尚民<br />\n出席映後談：黃瑋納 x 嚴尚民<br />\n主持：黃偉傑<br />\n<br />\n黃瑋納的《他們的海》和嚴尚民《赤手》分別選擇了觀眾陌生的故事題材&mdash;&mdash;漁民、無證難民拳手&mdash;&mdash;讓大家了解遠離城市的小眾。<br />\n<br />\n#2月24日 #生離與死別<br />\n《忘語花》李心悅<br />\n《艷陽天》葉嘉麟<br />\n出席映後談：李心悅 x 葉嘉麟<br />\n主持：黃修平<br />\n<br />\n為人父母，要跟子女生離死別。世間大概沒有比這更難過的事。<br />\n<br />\n#2月26日 #節奏就是一切<br />\n《至少在夢裏》卓亦謙 (III)<br />\n《網絡欺凌》李卓斌<br />\n出席映後談：卓亦謙 x 李卓斌<br />\n主持：嚴尚民、談晉霖<br />\n<br />\n卓亦謙的《至少在夢裏》和李卓斌的《網絡欺凌》同樣是關於校園裏自卑自憐的學生，用幻想逃避現實的殘酷。《至少在夢裏》由電影報刊辦電影評級為三級，不適合18歲以下人士觀看，敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\n**<span class=\"small\">每部短片可供觀影時間為一個月（例如2月1日播放的短片會在3月1日下架，如此類推）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">節目詳情：</span></span><a href=\"http://www.freshwave.hk/?a=group&amp;id=community\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.freshwave.hk%2F%3Fa%3Dgroup%26id%3Dcommunity&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=abf8521b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.freshwave.hk/?a=group&amp;id=community</a><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n#2月至5月<br />\n#逢星期一三五 <br />\n#晚上8時播映<br />\n#9時半映後談</span><br />\n<br />\n噤落去<span class=\"red\">節目詳情</span>嗰度 入邊有每套微電影嘅Vimeo link<br />\n<span class=\"large\">開口埋口本土 依家唔使錢俾你喺Vimeo 睇新導演嘅短片作品 g chi 下啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3d7db5678cb3bae15416db08587f65789728b3","tid":2417363,"uid":376697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T22:47:43.000Z","msg":"P牌狗咁早出post 撚有人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d5685118801dc4867633f0bc4631ea19ca9401","tid":2417363,"uid":376697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T22:48:22.000Z","msg":"有黃修平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b813dae06dfc46610f3ae0096e22dc4d082eb8f6","tid":2417363,"uid":376697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T22:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要沉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2854eb004a0a4adf7cdee982090debd9e6f821e","tid":2417363,"uid":339397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11745908b946d597b9d5af81a678df4fc2cdb3e6","tid":2417363,"uid":376697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T22:46:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">FB post link:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116437285041244/posts/4064716206879979/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116437285041244%2Fposts%2F4064716206879979%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c07974ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.face